title: Static Analysis

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from external storage.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows access to the list of accounts in the Accounts Service.

android.permission.USE_BIOMETRIC.description: Allows an app to use device supported biometric modalities.

android.permission.USE_FINGERPRINT.description: This constant was deprecated in API level 28. Applications should request USE_BIOMETRIC instead

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

manifest_analysis.title:
Broadcast Receiver (com.google.firebase.iid.FirebaseInstanceIdReceiver) is Protected by a permission, but the protection level of the permission should be checked.
Permission: com.google.android.c2dm.permission.SEND
[android:exported=true]
manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

playstore_details.title: Bitcoin Wallet BitBucks
playstore_details.description:
BitBucks mission is to give people from all over the world a simple and fast way to pay with bitcoin on their smartphones. Paying with the Bitcoin Wallet from BitBucks is both simple and innovative:

Simply pay with bitcoin to the phone number of a friend or scan the QR code of a participating merchant – and all within seconds. With BitBucks, long waiting times of Blockchain transactions become a matter of the past. As fast as the Lightning Network  and yet far more user-friendly!

Even if the payee does not have the BitBucks wallet yet, the bitcoin payment will be made instantly and added to the account after registration. That’s how easy mobile payments with bitcoin can be on your smartphone. Due to it’s simple interface and easy handling, BitBucks is even suitable for the stationary Retail!


Key features of BitBucks include:

* Payments with Bitcoin instantly to phone numbers

* Bitcoin Payments in Retail

* Payments in all currencies

* Simple and secure payments from everywhere

* Send bitcoins to friends and local businesses

* Make payments without high fees


We at BitBucks are intensively dealing with the future of crypto currencies and in this context are providing a solution which integrates Bitcoin into everyday life. We strongly believe that payments are the key to achieve this goal!


In just three simple steps you can pay (almost) everything with bitcoin:

Step 1: Get the mobile payment app BitBucks Wallet from the App Store

Step 2: Top-up your BitBucks account by sending BTC to your Bitcoin wallet address

Step 3: Simply pay with bitcoin to phone numbers of friends or merchants


BITCOIN - MONEY OF THE INTERNET 

Bitcoins true purpose is for payments - this is what we at BitBucks are convinced of. However to maintain it's key properties of being a highly secure censorship-resistant payment system - a decentralized settlement network - Bitcoin needs the Blockchain. 

Despite all its advantages in terms of security and decentralization, the Blockchain does not intrinsically make Bitcoin an adequate means of payment.

REGISTRATION

This is where BitBucks comes in! The Bitcoin Wallet enables instant payments with bitcoin. Users register at BitBucks just by entering their phone numbers followed by a validation code sended to them via sms.

Afterwards users can top-up their BitBucks account with bitcoin by using any other Bitcoin wallet. Every transaction within the BitBucks app, as well as the top-up of the account, are free of charge. 

SECURITY & PRIVACY

BitBucks facilitates the storage and exchange of bitcoins, as any wallet does. All bitcoins within BitBucks are stored on multi-signature addresses. Vaults securely store the keys, and to gain access additional custodians are required.

PAYMENTS

BitBucks supports nealry every monetary system arount the world and that's why payments within the Bitcoin Wallet are calculated in any selected currency.

We are keen on adapting Bitcoin into everyday life. Yet, we recommend every user that they should not store all their Bitcoin saving in the BitBucks app. Our Bitcoin wallet should be seen like a real wallet not like an another Bank account. The wallet should only hold as much bitcoin/ money as is needed for everyday use.

BITBUCKS IN RETAIL - A BITCOIN WALLET FOR THE WORLD 

BitBucks represents a profitable alternative not only to cash but also to other digital payment services (credit cards), as it speeds up the payment process on the one hand and requires lower fees on the other.

BitBucks thinks globally! Especially for countries of the global south, which are struggling with a strong inflation of their own currency, Bitcoin as a means of payment could bring real added value.

In countries with elaborated and widely spread banking services BitBucks is a cool and fast alternative way to do payments between family, friends and small businesses.


Download the Bitcoin Wallet from BitBucks now on Android or visit our Website: https://www.bitbucks.io
